{"tid":1261121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被警員搜身　「霸氣男」質問警察：有無宣誓過保護市民？憑乜對港人開槍？","createTime":"2019-06-27T05:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:15:44.000Z","uid":22575,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0163e844049ff596da83ad1ed48f11008d47e11a","tid":1261121,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"大批示威者昨晚（26日）起包圍灣仔警察總部，警方今日凌晨清場，事件中有1人被捕，60人被登記身份證資料。立場新聞直播時拍攝時，凌晨有市民行經灣仔軒尼斯道附近時，被4、5名警察截停搜身。該名市民當面與警方理論，批評警察濫權猶如內地城管、公安，侵犯港人自由。他又厲聲責罵警員：「你哋喺警校裡面有無宣誓過？！有無宣誓過要服務同埋保護香港市民？！To protect and to serve Hong Kong people?」、「（警員）1338，你答我！你答唔到啦嘛？！」<br />\n<br />\n有網民將該名男子稱作「霸氣市民」，讚揚他「零粗口」罵走警察。最終警察沒有回應並離開現場，惟該名男子繼續跟隨其後，對警員高叫：「著住制服，你都係人！你哋憑乜可以亂打人？對香港人開槍？」、「你哋唔係工具！唔係國家的殺人機器！」<br />\n<br />\n男子又質問警員，「你覺唔覺得羞恥？」、「我哋爭取應得的權利，我哋有無咁深仇大恨？！」。他勸警方，「你要記得自己咩人！你係香港人！我同你無分別！」<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，雖然該名男子厲聲質問了警方近10分鐘，他全程沒有說一句粗口，亦未有使用侮辱性的語句。<br />\n<br />\n男子其後接受《立場》記者訪問時表示，他當時只是上前與警員理論，就被警員無理搜身，他不知道之後會否被警方追究。但他指，香港近年的情況已越來越差，香港人無辦法不走出來。<br />\n<br />\n男子又指，問題始終源於政府、中央對香港人的肆意打壓，始作俑者並非警察，警察也只是執行命令，「但你們執行命令時，可唔可以唔打人個頭？可唔可以唔好打甘大力？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ke1lNZGzNOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fke1lNZGzNOE&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=fd8a7916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ke1lNZGzNOE</a><br />\n<br />\nCredit : <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%90%9C%E8%BA%AB-%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E7%94%B7-%E8%B3%AA%E5%95%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E9%81%8E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E6%86%91%E4%B9%9C%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D/?fbclid=IwAR3ieoc3CJn-Tdj3iDfU3RZHeC4_qFMePNUrLhVZ0oHngMBH-RcPQAgph2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25BA%25AB-%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%2586%2591%25E4%25B9%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ieoc3CJn-Tdj3iDfU3RZHeC4_qFMePNUrLhVZ0oHngMBH-RcPQAgph2s&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=0ba1d9a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25BA%25AB-%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%2586%2591%25E4%25B9%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ieoc3CJn-Tdj3iDfU3RZHeC4_qFMePNUrLhVZ0oHngMBH-RcPQAgph2s&h=03d22d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%90%9C%E8%BA%AB-%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E7%94%B7-%E8%B3%AA%E5%95%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E9%81%8E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E6%86%91%E4%B9%9C%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D/?fbclid=IwAR3ieoc3CJn-Tdj3iDfU3RZHeC4_qFMePNUrLhVZ0oHngMBH-RcPQAgph2s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉"},{"pid":"721dfcb31ff6332ca91f2f5e9c36154b4168fe64","tid":1261121,"uid":213848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:56:45.000Z","msg":"推 超霸氣"},{"pid":"256cae24103a3240b123c1c091873fc6349d6d91","tid":1261121,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:58:38.000Z","msg":"希望佢平安"},{"pid":"3633652039529d68ad71d77427f6e740cfef257f","tid":1261121,"ui