faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf96232befb61c02caaf35c3f0615c57f4f2ac5","tid":1261121,"uid":801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"佢係網台booom成員叫阿霸<br />\n 係四年前已經有蘋果動「霸氣哥」片段<br />\n所以今次絕對唔係搏上位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bIbQ_K4ZH00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbIbQ_K4ZH00&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=71831708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bIbQ_K4ZH00</a>  <br />\n上星期呢條片前五分鐘已經講到哽咽<br />\n請珍惜為香港發聲既人<br />\n多多支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}